author: Tal Axelrod
title: Texans plan to turn out Saturday calling to reopen the country
description: A group of Texans will protest at the Texas state capitol in Austin Saturday for a “You Can’t Close America” rally as demonstrators across the country rally against stay at home orders and other social distancing measures.
content:
A group of Texans will protest at the Texas state capitol in Austin Saturday for a You Cant Close America rally as demonstrators across the country rally against stay-at-home orders and other social distancing measures amid the coronavirus pandemic.
